<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-8 col-lg-offset-3 col-sm-offset-2 text-center">
            <h2>YOUR MOST CURRENT SUBMISSION</h2>
            <hr class="star-primary">
            <p>The latest image you supplied via Evernote</p>
            <p>The weight Evernote extracted from this image:</p>
            <p>This means your current BMI is:</p>
