            <p class="small">Open your Evernote app now or when you're at the store and it will be all right there for you.</p>
            <p ><%= image_tag "profile.png", class: "img-responsive", style: "margin: 0 auto;" %></p>
        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-8 col-lg-offset-3 col-sm-offset-2 text-center">
            <h2>Treat yourself to some delicious food!</h2>
            <hr class="star-primary">
            <p>Easy and convenient, get all the food delivered to your door: 
            <%= link_to image_tag(image_path("LeShopMigros.JPG"), class: "img", size: "100"),'http://www.leshop.ch/leshop/Main.do/direct/en/ean/95360', :target => "_blank"  %> </p>
